  <brief_title>The Impact of Interactive, Multifaceted Approach Education on Congenital Cataract</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Impact of Interactive, Multifaceted Approach Education on Parental Anxiety, Knowledge and Satisfaction for Congenital Cataract: A Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
